# Note: numba, pillow-heif, and opencv-python-headless are not available as
# Debian packages (or lack required modules). They are installed automatically
# via pip by the postinst script.
Description: Spectra 6 e-ink image server for Hokku/Huessen frames
 Converts and serves images for Hokku e-paper frames using
 Floyd-Steinberg dithering to the 6-color Spectra 6 palette.
 Supports JPEG, PNG, WebP, HEIC, and other image formats.
 Includes fair image rotation and server-driven sleep scheduling.
